ygData.msgSnippet: I hear that if you walk out of unrest, and go straight in the water, that the entrance is right near ther. I belive I got this info off of this mailing list,
ygData.messageBody:
I hear that if you walk out of unrest, and go straight in the water, that
the entrance is right near ther.

I belive I got this info off of this mailing list, but I am way to low to
go, so I'll settle for Unrest.

Wenaddar 17th level bard of Cazic-Thule
